{"narrativeText":"You press forward into the deeper shadows of the warehouse, maintaining your cautious and alert demeanor. Your ears pick up the telltale sounds of more giant rats rustling amid the discarded crates and sacks. The stench of mildew is stronger here, mingling with the unmistakable musk of the vermin.

