{"narrativeText":"You intently maneuver your shield, using its bulk to crowd the remaining giant rat. With deft movements, you press forward, keeping the shield up and using it as both a barrier and a weapon in its own right. The rat finds itself stifled, its attempts to move curtailed by your unyielding defense.

