{"narrativeText":"You stride over to the large figure, your intent clear as you approach. He notices your presence and nods, a glint of curiosity in his eye as he sizes you up. "Hail, traveler," he says with a friendly yet commanding tone. "I see you've an air of purpose about you. What brings you to my table?"

