With the ledger safely in hand, the possibilities intrigue you. Do you wish to delve deeper into its contents now or secure it as you continue your search for more clues?","stateChanges":{"itemsGained":[{"characterId":"01KKZCA18K05KZ6MMNJQGFQ1XQ","item":{"id":"item-tattered-ledger","name":"Tattered Ledger","category":"quest","description":"A ledger containing records of transactions and potential contacts tied to the bandit operations.","value":50,"quantity":1}}]}}

