{"narrativeText":"With your orders given, Bjorik efficiently marshals the men into action, using the tools to establish the camp's structure and build a comforting fire. As the scene hums with the bustle of preparation, you beckon the half-elf and the dwarf to follow you.

Moving to the edge of the clearing, the atmosphere shifts to one of quietude and shadow, the forest's serenity a stark contrast to the earlier chaos. The half-elf and dwarf walk alongside, a faint curiosity intermingled with respect in their eyes.

Standing there, away from prying ears, what do you wish to discuss with them?","stateChanges":{}}

